421
00:44:26,920 --> 00:44:28,990
Aku punya izin!

422
00:44:44,010 --> 00:44:45,160
Sekarang.

423
00:44:47,980 --> 00:44:50,140
Tunggu. Lampu darurat akan nyala segera.

424
00:44:50,140 --> 00:44:53,400
